ygData.subject: RE:Kunark Level 21
ygData.msgSnippet: With Selos, I have only attracted the attention of one of the spiders once. Even then it only lightly tapped me with a couple spells before I was out of range.
ygData.messageBody:
With Selos, I have only attracted the attention of one of the spiders once.
Even then it only lightly tapped me with a couple spells before I was out of
range. I have to admit that is scared me silly until I zoned but I only
lost about 1/2 bubble of health before I got away from it. I was of course
heading toward the Lake of Ill Omen which looks like it is easier to get to
than the Swamp of No hope.

On a second note: That was a great song Reed! I thought it was great

Rylos Darkmadrigal of E'ci Bard of the 23rd chorus
